edu.vserver.exercises.stub
Class StubDataFilesHandler

java.lang.Object
  edu.vserver.exercises.stub.StubDataFilesHandler

final class StubDataFilesHandler
extends java.lang.Object

A class handling file operations to store data needed by the stub-versions persistence layer. Stores and loads ExerciseData- and SubmissionInfo -instances. All files are stored inside the folder returned by #getStubResourceBaseDir().

Author:
Riku Haavisto
